'''''Sinking Sands''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Gana]] yo mu 2010,<ref>https://www.nydjlive.com/leila-djansis-sinking-sands-makes-it-to-cnn-as-must-see-african-movies-of-the-21st-century/</ref> yanditswe yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Leila Djansi, ikinwamo Jimmy Jean-Louis, Ama Abebrese, Emmanuel Yeboah A. na Yemi Blaq<ref>https://face2faceafrica.com/article/ghanaian-born-award-winning-director-leila-djansi-s-hit-movie-sinking-sands-opens-in-new-york-city-theaters-this-week</ref> . Iyi filime yakiriye ibihembo icyenda  kandi yatsindiye ibihembo 3 muri Afurika ya Movie Academy Awards 2011, harimo ibihembo bya ''Best Screenplay'' & ''Best Makeup'' <ref>https://www.talkafricanmovies.com/sinking-sands/</ref><ref>https://villagerainbows.com/2010/11/08/sinking-sands-setting-a-new-standard/</ref>. 

== Ikibanza ==
Iyi filime ivuga amateka y'abashakanye, Jimah na Pabi, ishyingiranwa ryabo rikaba urugomo no guhohoterwa iyo Jimah ahindutse isura mu mpanuka yo mu rugo<ref>https://www.thecherrypicks.com/films/sinking-sands/</ref>.<ref>https://www.allmovie.com/movie/sinking-sands-v536856/cast-crew</ref> 

== Kwakira ==
Iyi filime yakiriwe neza nabantu benshi banenga firime nyafurika hamwe na NollywoodForever.com basoza bavuga ko "Filime nziza nabatura mbikuye ku mutima<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/Sinking_Sands/10913686</ref>. Ibi birerekana abo bantu bose bafite ibitekerezo bigufi bizera ko ukeneye glitz, glamour na brazilian kuboha kugirango ukore firime nziza utakora<ref>https://alchetron.com/Sinking-Sands</ref>. Ubukorikori muri firime bwari buteye ubwoba no gushimwa. Gukina byari ingingo nkuko byari bimeze kuri sinema.<ref>https://www.naijarules.com/threads/sinking-sands-new-film-from-leila-djansi.37744/</ref><ref>http://www.zimfilmfest.co.zw/screening/main/screening-sinkingsands.html</ref> "
